#: src/callbacks.c:137
msgid ""
"Ground plane detected in model. T_ant results will overcount ground effects. "
"Free-space models are standard for antenna temperature evaluation."
msgstr ""
"Mudelis tuvastati maatasand. T_ant tulemused arvestavad maapinna mõju üle. "
"Vaba ruumi mudelid on antennitemperatuuri hindamiseks standardsed."

#: src/callbacks.c:153
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Max gain at θ=%.0f° (%.0f° from XY plane). Convention assumes beam in XY "
"plane with observation elevation set by spinbutton."
msgstr ""
"Maksimaalne võimendus θ=%.0f° juures (%.0f° XY tasandist). Kokkuleppe "
"kohaselt on kiir XY tasandil ja vaatluse tõstenurk määratakse keritatavast "
"nupust."

